---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Все новости"
permalink: /news/
---
<div class="container page-content">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Лента новостей</h1>
    <p>Официальные заявления и пресс-релизы</p>
  </header>

  <div class="search-container">
    <input type="search" id="search-input" placeholder="Поиск по новостям..." aria-label="Поиск">
    <div id="search-results" class="search-results-dropdown" style="display: none;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="news-list">
    {% for article in collections.news %}
      <article class="news-list-item">
        <div class="news-meta">
          <time datetime="{{ article.date | dateFormat }}">{{ article.date | dateFormat }}</time>
        </div>
        <h2><a href="{{ article.url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a></h2>
        {% if article.data.description %}
          <p>{{ article.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="news-tags">
          {% for tag in article.data.tags %}
            <span class="tag">#{{ tag }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
